ore":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:51:44.000Z","msg":"日本威士忌，得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5a99b226e42860d93dbb9cb244fcec759c1463","tid":1587074,"uid":61267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:12:30.000Z","msg":"終於正常媒體有關注<br />\n<br />\n個問題其實講左2-3年<br />\n<br />\n請按link 睇圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/142626_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F142626_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBnwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=5bab8d51\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/142626_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/142626_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F142626_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b4a882e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b6eef053418285cfd7c1cd2084daa6791cb0db7","tid":1587074,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T23:44:10.000Z","msg":"識飲根本唔會飲日本威士忌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n貪新鮮試吓就得，用嚟請客見人攞支日威出嚟，盞比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18aeed241842d5f2509fad2d4b442e661ff0ddf7","tid":1587074,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}